"{\"uid\": \"bobfm.co.uk-artistic-director-denies-writing-scene-ridiculed-opening-of-olympic-games-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics organization has denied any intention to offend religious groups after criticism from Christians and conservatives over the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.7806639692069047, \"rank\": 0.22814832851041308, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At issue is a sequence that has been interpreted as a reference toaLast SupperLeonardo da Vinci's painting depicts the moment Jesus Christ announced that an apostle would betray him.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9991195964648446, \"rank\": 0.0008811793282412364, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The scene was attended by DJ and producer Barbara Boch - an icon of the LGBTQ+ community - surrounded by artistspullAnd the dancers.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Barbara\", \"score\": 0.9172270629488859, \"rank\": 0.08910235594919959, \"text\": \"Barbara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Barbara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Barbara\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the artistic director of the ceremony, Thomas Joly, denied this today, Sunday.Last SupperIt served as inspiration for the number.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 526, \"end\": 532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9999832005932183, \"rank\": 9.270419196761021e-06, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea was to have a big pagan party linked to the Olympian gods,\\\" Julie told BFMTV.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twelve_Olympians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.402792323754054e-28, \"text\": \"Olympian gods\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twelve_Olympians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twelve_Olympians\"}, {\"begin\": 698, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Furthermore, the presence of a masked actor as Dionysus suggests that this was not a representation of the moment of Jesus' betrayal.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.738251314774004e-18, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9987105943251341, \"rank\": 0.0012910701962794533, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, religious conservatives around the world have condemned the clip, with the French Catholic Bishops' Conference denouncing \\\"scenes of mockery\\\" that they said mocked Christianity - a sentiment shared by the spokeswoman for the Russian Foreign Ministry, Maria Zakharova.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.977808929707286, \"rank\": 0.022681106536483205, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9755343043937049, \"rank\": 0.025079272258409616, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"score\": 0.999999999875854, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russian Foreign Ministry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\"}, {\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maria Zakharova\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Anglican community in Egypt expressed its \\\"deep regret\\\" on Sunday, noting that the ceremony could cause the IOC to lose its \\\"distinctive sporting identity and humanitarian mission.\\\"\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"score\": 0.9761126188132171, \"rank\": 0.024452181792026496, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\"}, {\"begin\": 1230, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.722832880348299e-13, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolie denied any intention to confront religious groups and said the aim was to celebrate diversity and praise the festival and French cuisine.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1433, \"end\": 1447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French cuisine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_cuisine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Paris 2024 spokeswoman Anne Descamps was questioned about the protests during an IOC press conference.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.0734566060029537e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}, {\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.722832880348299e-13, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is clear that there was absolutely no intention to disrespect any religious community.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, I believe that [com] \\\"Thomas Joly, we really tried to celebrate the tolerance of society,\\\" said Descamps.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Given the results of the surveys we shared, we believe that this ambition has been achieved.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people were offended, we are of course very sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Jolie explained his intentions to The Associated Press after the ceremony: \\\"My intention was not to be subversive, nor to mock or shock.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1969, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"sc